ent with a top-down\nhydrocarbon chemistry, in which large polyatomic molecules or small\ncarbonaceous grains are photo-destroyed into smaller hydrocarbon\nmolecules/precursors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 01:32:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
