on stages of Ne$^{7+}$-Ne$^{9+}$,\nwhile the DCH spectroscopy from lower charge states Ne$^{2+}$-Ne$^{6+}$ are\nmuch weaker. With the increase of x-ray photon energy, the contributions from\nthe lower charge states become larger.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 10:03:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-10"}
